    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.80)) + wp.exp((v1 + 0.99 * v0 + 0.82)))
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.47)) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.66 * tmp + 0.82)))
    v2 = ((0.70 - wp.abs(v0 + 0.90)) * 0.85)
    v0 = (0.35 / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.72) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.63)))
